snippet.textDisplay:
So...

You changed names, so you can't make the Fa Ping joke. In fact, you seem to have taken ALL of the humor out, notably Mushu.

You seem to have taken most, if not all of the singing out (which normally I'd be glad for, but Mulan had two pretty memorable songs in it).

You pointlessly added wire-fu and more outright magic/superpowers to it.

Nope, I'm out.

READ PLEASE! Just like Mary Poppins, Beauty & Beast and Aladdin, Disney always starts with more shitty trailers to get people mad and later surprised... Yes, Reflection was really emotional. However, all of you who are missing Mushu, it actually makes much more sense that he is a bird (phoenix) here, so he can serve as A CONTRAST to evil falcon. Lacking singing also does make sense - how on Earth you expect people to sing happy songs while they are GOING TO WAR?!?! ITS DISNEY THEY KNOW WHAT THEY ARE DOING AND EVERY REMAKE WILL BE GOOD!

PS I just hope that the dolls will be good & it will include phoenix figure, since that dolls which Hasbro made for Aladdin are really trashy & they didn't feature any pet
